<emphasis id="B93A3657FFC09E1E81C221BB383A49D1" bold="true" box="[136,330,157,184]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="73">Curtia tenuifolia</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFDF97B4FFC09E1E801B21BB3B2649D1" author="Knoblauch, E. F." box="[337,598,158,184]" pageId="12" pageNumber="73" pagination="323 - 357" refId="ref15849" refString="Knoblauch, E. F. (1894) Beitragezur Kenntniss der Gentianaceaea. Botanisches Centralblatt 60: 323 - 357." type="journal article" year="1894">Knoblauch (1894: 323)</bibRefCitation>
